high_descs: Turn around and go near to the sink.
Find the spoon on the sink.
Take the spoon and put into the sink and washed.
Take the spoon from the sink.
Then placed the spoon on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Clean the Spoon and placed on the Sink.

high_descs: In the toilet room turn around and take right to the sink.
Head towards the spoon and reach the spoon.
Pick the spoon from the sink.
Put the spoon on the sink and pour the water and clean the spoon.
Pick the cleaned spoon and keep it on top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick the spoon clean it and keep it on the sink

high_descs: Turn on the sink in the right side.
Put the spoon on the fruit in the wash in water.
Take it on the spoon and put it in the sink.
Take the spoon on the spoon in the clear water.
Take the spoon and put it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cleaning the spoon in the sink with pure water.
